snippet.title: Bloons TDX Trailer
snippet.description:
Bloons TDX is a fan game that is available now. Here are some things you can check out:

- 20 Towers, each with 3 upgrade paths.

- 8 Tracks with multiple play modes.

- 6 Unique Special Missions.

- Tons of New Bloon Types.

- And 100+ Achievements to unlock.

For more information on the game visit the links below. They might be updated with more information. Also check this channel often for potential game previews. Also a special shout out to Ninja Kiwi for being awesome.

ramafparty.com
